headline: Pot Stock Euphoria Vanishes as US Legalization Remains Elusive
summary: (Bloomberg) -- The stock market’s marijuana boom is over. And for the once high-flying cannabis industry, a euphoric dream of never-ending growth has turned into a survival nightmare as it navigates through the bust.
